```jsx
<Route
  path="/admin/algorithm-processor"
  element={

      <SuperAdminPanel />
    </ProtectedRoute>
  }
/>
```

Now when you click on "Algorithm Processor" in the sidebar, it will:
1. Navigate to `/admin/algorithm-processor`
2. The ProtectedRoute will verify you're a super_admin
3. SuperAdminPanel will render and show the AlgorithmDataProcessor component

The navigation should work perfectly now without any logout issues!
